javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest, javax.servlet.ServletRequest
public class AAIServletRequest
extends javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequestWrapper

HttpServletRequestWrapper to provide proper user information overriding HttpServletRequest.getRemoteUser() and HttpServletRequest.getUserPrincipal(); further provides AuthenticationContext

Author:
megger
See Also:
HttpServletRequest.getRemoteUser(), HttpServletRequest.getUserPrincipal(), getAuthenticationContext()
